{"tid":416210,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我已經放唔低你 如果當初我冇搵你 今日都唔會咁唔開心..","createTime":"2017-09-27T15:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T09:23:29.000Z","uid":137847,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0a1097fe0fe80c50993d5e5e77f0007ded68a6","tid":416210,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:12:48.000Z","msg":"無論你見唔見到都好<br />\n估唔估到係我又好 我知你應該有上連登<br />\n我都好想講我已經放唔低你<br />\n我仲會因為你一個回覆一個訊息而開心<br />\n我知呢刻我唔會再講任何嘢都唔會主動搵你<br />\n我驚我騷擾左你 <br />\n成日我都會呃自己你只不過唔得閒唔開心所以先唔搵我啫<br />\n但其實得我一個上心 永遠都係<br />\n又係嘅 你心裡面根本冇我<br />\n但點解要關心我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係自己諗太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好啦呻完繼續等佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494bfb324059a09274a951260998514471a60dd4","tid":416210,"uid":10330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"唔想再經歷依d情況<br />\n我已決定放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d297c9271df08def4665c15f3d4faa4dcef9fd24","tid":416210,"uid":81463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab209ec60d23db6eab6b30d46c30a0bf2d0a8f0e","tid":416210,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想再經歷依d情況<br />\n我已決定放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前有個愛幾年無疾而終<br />\n本來以為自己真係唔會再動情 <br />\n點知就瀨晒嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係垃圾"},{"pid":"15593be8989cc2db2854fcfc035f188a1a17a750","tid":416210,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote